I know it seems like I think there are more terribly designed champs than good ones but that isn't true. Everything not in the Best or Worst section I think is good or ok in design. It just I do think there are a few very well designed champions and some very badly designed champions. Just so you know I am not being 100% biased I play Janna quite often not because she is broken but because she is fun, but she is not well designed. I don't play jhin or lucian or Braum or illaoi but I do think as far as their role and identity they are very well designed. There is one champion that I think is the worst design of all though, I wonder if you can figure it out :P

